<div class='span12'>
<h2>Amikuzera [Der baskische Dialekt von Amikuze/Pays de Mixe, Pyrénées-Atlantiques] (Sonstiges)</h2>
<h3>Ursprünglich: Beiheft zu ASJU 28, 1995, 173-187</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2172'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
<h4>Autor(en)</h4>
<a href="/pers/2905-Martin_Haase" class="tag multiline" popup="true">Martin Haase</a>
<p class='space-l'></p>
<dl class='attribute_listing'>
